name: Everbilt 130 lb. Extension Spring Kit with Safety Cable
description: The Everbilt 130 lb. Extension Springs (2-Pack) are made of spring steel and designed to be mounted perpendicular above the horizontal track of the garage door. They stretch to provide lifting power for the garage door. The springs have a safety cable inside to prevent injury in case of accidental breakage.Ideal for single-car fiberglass doorsSafe length when stretched of 67 in. according to ansi/dasma 103Able to lift garage doors up to 130 lb.Color-coded yellow to indicate weight-bearing capacityDurable and tested to open and close the door at least 10,000 timesCable clamp included
